data.description: Situated on a highly warranted 8,000+ square foot corner lot in the very sought after SoSo neighborhood, you don't want to miss this. Talk about options and opportunities for different buyers, this home is the perfect space for a primary residence, an investment property (AIRBNB ALLOWED) or even new development. NEW: roof, pool, impact windows, appliances, solar panels, and landscape. Just two blocks from the intracoastal - imagine yourself on sunrise and sunset walks. Opportunity to open up the kitchen as previously done in many of the same floor plans in the neighborhood. 5 minute drive to downtown West Palm, home to many of the city's best restaurants, shops, etc. and a hop, skip, and a jump right over the bridge to Palm Beach. Run, don't walk to this piece of paradise!
